airtrafficcontrol.app.exceptions

Class InvalidOptionNumberException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • airtrafficcontrol.app.exceptions.InvalidOptionNumberException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class InvalidOptionNumberException
extends java.lang.Exception
    Exception thrown when it was received an invalid number of option (that is not between 1 and the number of the last option in an OptionsMenu) in an operation which involves only the numbers of the options available in a certain OptionsMenu.
